30 general election ballot in the order listed in IC 3-11-2-12,
31 IC 3-11-2-12.4, IC 3-11-2-12.5, IC 3-11-2-12.7(b), IC 3-11-2-12.9(a),
32 IC 3-11-2-12.9(c), IC 3-11-2-13(a) through IC 3-11-2-13(c),
33 IC 3-11-2-14(a), IC 3-11-2-14(d), and IC 3-11-2-14(e). Each office and
34 public question may have a separate screen, or the offices and public
35 questions may be listed in a continuous column either vertically or
36 horizontally.
